Upstream Components
================================================================================

This project orchestrates the following upstream models and tools. Each
remains under its own license; redistributors must comply with all of them.

* TripoSR
    https://github.com/VAST-AI-Research/TripoSR
    License: MIT
    Copyright (c) VAST-AI-Research

* TRELLIS
    https://github.com/microsoft/TRELLIS
    License: MIT
    Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation

* Segment Anything 2 (SAM 2.1)
    https://github.com/facebookresearch/sam2
    License: Apache 2.0
    Copyright (c) Meta Platforms

* Blender
    https://www.blender.org/
    License: GPL v2 / GPL v3
    Used as an external tool via headless invocation; this project's source
    code is NOT linked into Blender. Models exported by Blender are not
    derivative works of Blender itself.

* Blender MCP Addon
    https://github.com/ahujasid/blender-mcp
    License: MIT
    Copyright (c) ahujasid
